%F A180445 x = sqrt((sqrt(6*(y^2) - 5) + 1)/2) = (sqrt(2^(z + 3) - 7) + 1)/2; y = {1, 3, 7, 29, 6761} and z = (A060728(n) - 3) = A215795(n) = {0, 1, 2, 4, 12}. - _Raphie Frank_, Jun 23 2013
